{"word":"παρεδρεύω","slug":"παρεδρεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παρεδρεύω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:πάρεδρος'><el>πάρεδρος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to sit constantly beside, attend constantly, be always near</i>, <a href='S:Latin'>Lat.</a> <el>assidere</el>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of judges, <i>to be an assessor</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}